item.p:
NewPasswd. The new password to set. Should be ""
            if the server is to generate the password. In this case,
            the result will be {ok, GenPasswd}.

type.v:
SearchOption = {base, string()} | {filter, filter()} | {scope, scope()}
	| {attributes, [string()]} | {deref, dereference()} |
	| {types_only, boolean()} | {timeout, integer()}
